title: Summer Magic by Rochelle Alers
description:
Caryn Edwards needs to heal the wounds left by her ugly divorce and recover from a bad case of career burnout as a home economics teacher, so she rents a summer house on North Carolina's Marble Island. 

What she doesn't bargain for is handsome developer Logan Prescott, who will unexpectedly be sharing the house with her. But Logan has his own demons to deal with, and no intention of letting Caryn distract him--even if she is the most tempting woman he's ever met.

Genre: Romance
